  "description": "This individual is a human bartender of early middle age, identified by steady brown eyes and a composed, appraising gaze. Brown hair is kept in a practical shortknot that leaves the face unobstructed, emphasizing a square jaw and prominent cheekbones. Bronze skin shows ingrained calluses across the hands and faint old nicks along the knuckles, consistent with long service in a working bar. Their manner is orderly and unshowy, marked by quick arithmetic, strict portioning, and a firm intolerance for disorder at the counter.",
